---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About GearCouple';
const description = 'Learn more about GearCouple – your destination for matching couple outfits, love quotes, and relationship inspiration.';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About GearCouple</h1>
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="/assets/about-couple-gear.webp" alt="A happy couple wearing matching outfits" width="330">
      <figcaption>
        Celebrating love, one match at a time.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    
    <p>Welcome to <strong>GearCouple.com</strong>, where style meets sentiment. We believe that love is an adventure best shared, and how you express that bond should be as unique as your relationship.</p>
    
    <p>Our journey began with a simple idea: that being a couple is something to celebrate out loud. Whether it is through the perfect matching hoodies that say "we are a team" without speaking a word, or through the heartfelt quotes that capture the butterflies of your first date, we are here to help you tell your love story.</p>
    
    <p><strong>What We Do</strong></p>
    <p>We specialize in curating the best in couple fashion—from T-shirts to accessories—alongside a deep library of romantic messages and relationship quotes. We know that sometimes it is hard to find the right words (or the right outfit) to show how much you care. That is where we come in.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Our Mission</strong></p>
    <p>To bring couples closer together. Whether you are looking for a fun gift for your anniversary, the perfect caption for your Valentine's Day post, or just a way to coordinate your style for a weekend getaway, GearCouple is your companion in love and life.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for letting us be a small part of your big love story.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em; /* Adjusted slightly */
    width: 100%; /* Ensures responsiveness within the max-width */
    height: auto;
  }

  .about-image figcaption {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .about-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }
  }
</style>
